graphql.query:
query ConnectConsoleLoginWithPassword($input: ConnectConsoleLoginWithPasswordInput!) {
  connectConsoleLoginWithPassword(input: $input) {
    _token
    connect_id
    device_is_restricted
    device_is_verified
    device_limit_exceeded
    device_restricted_duration
    device_token_expired_at
    device_verification_required
    id
    image_url
    password_token_expired_at
    password_verification_required
    user_first_name
    user_is_ban
    user_is_restricted
    user_last_name
    user_middle_name
  }
}
